                                                    <h3 class="mt-20">Using the grid <a href="" id="Using-the-grid"
                                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h3>
                                                    <p>
                                                    Nest <code>.container-fluid</code> inside the <code>.modal-body</code> to use the UX4G grid system within a modal. Use the grid system classes as you would anywhere else after that.
                                                    </p>
                                                    <div class="code_bg rounded p-3">
                                                        <button class="btn btn-outline-primary float-end"
