                                                    <h3 class="mt-20">Change animation <a href="" id="Change-animation"
                                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h3>
                                                    <p>
                                                    The transform state of the <code>.modal-dialog </code> before the modal <code>fade-in</code> animation is determined by the <code>$modal-fade-transform</code> variable, and the transform state of the <code>.modal-dialog after</code> the modal <code>fade-in</code> animation is determined by the <code>$modal-show-transform</code> variable.
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>
                                                    For instance, you can use <code>$modal-fade-transform: scale(.8)</code> if you want a zoom-in motion.
                                                    </p>
                                                    <h3>Remove animation <a href="" id="Remove-animation"
                                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h3>
                                                    <p>For modals that simply appear rather than fade in to view, remove
                                                        the <code>.fade</code> class from your modal markup.</p>
